      • create

        public static Sensor<java.net.URI> create(SensorParams p)
        Factory method to allow creation through the SensorFactory in the Sensor.create(SensorFactory, SensorParams) method of the parent Sensor class. This indirection allows the decoration of the returned Sensor type by wrapping it in an HTMSensor (which is the current implementation but could be any wrapper).
        Parameters:
        p - the SensorParams which describe connection or source data details.
        Returns:
        the Sensor.
